Additional Information
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
For information on 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
application
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 fees for the common carrier services, or for information on 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
application 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
and 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
regulatory
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 fees for cable television, mass media, engineering and technology, field operations or private radio services,
the Commission has prepared a number of informative Fee Filing Guides. These Guides are available from the Commission's
Public Service Division, from field office locations and can be downloaded from the Internet (ftp@fcc.gov). For
additional information, please contact the Public Service Division's Fees Hotline at (202) 632&hyph;FEES (3337),
or write to: Federal Communications Commission, ATTN: Public Service Division, 1919 M Street, NW., Washington,
DC, 20554.
